item.title: Commissioned management of Rubycamp 2023 from Shimane Prefecture
item.description: On Mar 15, 2023 Shimane Prefecture commissioned the operation for the Rubycamp 2023. We have been operating Ruby training camps since 2011, and this is our 13th year.
